    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a solid option for anyone seeking dependable daily transportation. Mechanically, it has been well-maintained with regular oil changes and recent brake service, ensuring it starts and runs reliably every day. However, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some paint fading on the hood, and a small dent on the rear passenger door. The interior is clean but shows typical wear on the driver's seat and floor mats. If you are looking for a functional, honest car that prioritizes performance over aesthetics, this is an excellent choice.",
