      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been super well-loved over the years\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road. It runs like a dream and is ready for its next adventure with you! Drop me a message if you want to come take it for a spin!",
