      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This 2018 Lexus RX 350 is a stunning example of luxury and dependability. Finished in a sophisticated Eminent White Pearl, the exterior retains a deep, glossy luster, with only the minor, inevitable stone chips consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the parchment leather seats are supple and free of tears, while the walnut wood trim remains vibrant and scratch-free. All technological features, including the navigation system, heated and ventilated seats, and the premium audio suite, are in perfect working order. Under the hood, the V6 engine runs flawlessly, backed by a comprehensive service history from certified technicians. The ride is whisper-quiet, and the tires have ample tread remaining. This vehicle has been smoke-free and garage-kept, offering a turnkey experience for the next owner who appreciates a well-preserved, premium SUV.",
